_*Update - Workaround Provided by [~dshekhawat] (it still would be better to address the issue at hand)*_

If you change your "computer name" , please also set the same in a file call "configuration.xml" inside the instance. There is a floppy drive attached to your windows instance, if you browse inside it, you should see a file "configuration.xml" , please open this file in a text editor and set your "computer name" under following (without the quotes):

{code}
<Hostname>"my computer name"</Hostname>
{code}
